"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## Set up a client\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/rEvdoHareFFwYMs5gslFW.PNG?height=874&width=1884)\\n\\n## Setting up to deploy to the blockchain\\n\\n![Alchemy essentially helps us broadcast our contract creation transaction so that it can be picked up by miners as quickly as possible](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/V88qHuDvhZEjCYfXylj_s.PNG?height=678&width=1659)\\n\\n![There are a few testnets out there and the one we'll be using is called \\\"Rinkeby\\\" which is run by the Ethereum foundation.In order to deploy to Rinkeby, we need fake ether.](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Nl5M6QxF-yUSC9IvksWA5.PNG?height=934&width=1792)\\n\\n![0x46419AeaDd20a6DFDBEb6a2034E5A31B2238B8ef, we deployed our smart contract to Rinkeby with address above using Alchemy API. ](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/c_hMPgUX6m1zwtR74NAU0.PNG?height=115&width=990)\\n\\n \\n \\n\\n![https://rinkeby.etherscan.io/address/0x46419AeaDd20a6DFDBEb6a2034E5A31B2238B8ef](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Fp5Ny522ga4wRYN4y4fCK.PNG?height=908&width=1823)\\n\\n## Using window.ethereum()\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/4qsRc1Lwhe-58xPksygNo.PNG?height=800&width=1868)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/8sth9Quvbggs5ZaaMRAHm.PNG?height=467&width=1435)\\n\\n## Read from the blockchain through our website\\n\\nWe can use address of our smart contract on Rinkeby that we uploaded using Alchemy. \\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/uQ_H0u0mR1YU89JBvwTCl.PNG?height=755&width=1543)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Rx3WuwDFhkWLVuZ7Mp4GT.PNG?height=694&width=1470)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640851955,\"title\":\"Day 2: Creating a Twitter-like Web 3.0 App\"},\"digest\":\"BT812ZRn8dn_RmgECoy4Ka_NB1gyrxgPu8vM_FApdeQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xB2C65d2941766a63697bA62e9b0e2ABD0a60F360\"